cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "OASIS-LLM: Adapting OASIS to Run with LLM Agents"
abstract: >-
  A research harness that adapts the OASIS image-norming procedure
  (Kurdi, Lozano, & Banaji, 2017) to vision-language model "agents",
  measuring how contemporary LLMs rate affective images on
  valence and arousal dimensions and comparing the results to the
  human MTurk norms.
authors:
